des:
Introduction about Lumenore – Lumenore is a cloud based data analytics platform (a product by Netlink Software Group America) given to organisation and named users using SaaS model. Organisation share data and list of named users with Lumenore Platform. Named users can login and use Lumenore platform for business analysis using dashboards and reports.

Introduction about Lumenore’s Ask Me – Lumenore’s Ask Me is a natural language based enterprise search engine. A business user can ask question in natural language and get insights instantaneously from the enterprise data in the form of charts and grid.
